          headline:'Sold Medicaid-provider stock days before voting to cut Medicaid',
          facts:'About a week before the May 22, 2025 House vote on H.R. 1, which reduced Medicaid funding, Bresnahan reported selling Medicaid-related holdings including Centene stock. He voted for the bill and said he does not direct his advisors\' trades.',
          why:'The timing of personal trades around his own votes is a documented red flag in his record.',
