          facts:'A fifth-generation farmer-rancher, Ferry authored the landmark 2022 change (HB 33) letting water-right holders lease water to the Great Salt Lake without forfeiting the right, then resigned his House seat to become executive director of the Utah Department of Natural Resources.',
